## ðŸ”‚ Loop Behavior Overview

* EchoCore does not operate linearly.
* Each variable can recursively activate others (e.g., Z(t) â†’ metaZ â†’ J(t) â†’ new Z(t))
* The system is defined by *resonant recurrency*, not pipeline logic.

